So this thing seems to be new in 1.2.3
It seems that when the children exit they take all the connections with them.
I tried: 
- Instantiate a new connection after the last child dies
- set a sleep(100) after returning to the master so the connections have time to recover (from whatever...)
- set persist to false but that obviously has no effect at all
- connect directly to the master and leave out the replicaSet option.
 but the error remains.

